本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:黃怡甄研究生(外文):Yi-chen Huang論文名稱:太陽能電池產業之專利佈局分析與績效評估論文名稱(外文):Patent portfolio analysis and performance evaluation for the solar cell industry指導教授:李國榮、江梓安指導教授(外文):Kuo-Jung Lee、Tzu-An Chiang學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立屏東商業技術學院系所名稱:企業電子化研究所學門:商業及管理學門學類:企業管理學類論文出版年:2011畢業學年度:99語文別:中文論文頁數:54中文關鍵詞:專利佈局、太陽能電池、績效評估外文關鍵詞:performance evaluation、solar cell、patent layout相關次數:

被引用:1點閱:454評分:下載:0書目收藏:0



在日漸高漲的環保意識與自然資源耗竭的問題下，本文以台灣太陽能中游的太陽能電池產業為主要的研究議題，探討其關鍵技術佈局與研發績效評估。本研究以專利數量作為績效評估的產出變數、公司的資本額與研發費用作為投入變數，使用TOPSIS評估法與AHP層級分析法，分析太陽能電池廠商之研發績效並加以排序。本研究發現在16家公司中研發績效排名前三名公司為中美晶、茂矽與新日光。其中中美晶的發展重點以H01與C30分類碼為重，其關鍵技術在太陽能電池的晶片、製程、模組與長晶爐體結構上的發展為主；而茂矽與新日光則以H01分類碼為重要佈局，發展以太陽能電池的晶片、製程、模組為重點。

Due to environmental consciousness and exhausted nature resources, this study investigates the key-technology layout and performance evaluation of the Taiwan solar cell companies in the mid-stream solar energy industry. To evaluate the performance of solar cell companies, this study uses the company capital and R&D expense as the input variables and the patent numbers of different critical technologies as the output variables. In addition, this study applies the method of TOPSIS and AHP to evaluate and rank the performance of solar cell companies. In this study, we can find, by the performance of solar cell companies, the top three of the sixteen companies are Saswafer, Mosel, and Neosolarpower. The development important fields of SAS are H01 and C30. The key technologies of this company are wafers, manufacture, module structures, and crystal growth furnaces. For the Mosel and NSP, they also focus on H01 and consider the solar cell wafer, process, and module structure as key technologies. Finally, I hope the analytical results of this study can provide a reference to strengthen the competitiveness of the Taiwan’s solar cell companies.

